Echoes


Echoes are one of five currencies on Identity V .


Contents


Overview [ ]


Echoes are a currency used to purchase dice, costumes, characters, pets, music, and Inspirations .


Shadows in the Flame [ ]


This event is triggered usually when players are low on Echoes, which would prompt them to buy more.



  
1388 Echoes: A-Tier Memory Sphere Costume of featured character;

  
300 Echoes: 300 Inspirations + Two most recent season essences




Obtaining [ ]


Echoes are bought from the in-game store. You can exchange for various items by obtaining Echoes. They appear to only be available for purchase through the mobile version.


The exchange rates for echoes are based on the player's region.


